name: Jamila Thomas
interests: Reading, Hiking, Live Music, Technology, Trail Running
summary: Jamila Thomas is a 35-year-old Senior Software Engineer in the Tech Industry based in Los Angeles, California, originally from Sacramento. She is an educated woman from Stanford University, fluent in English, Spanish, and Swahili. Jamila is agnostic, politically liberal, and is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship. She identifies as a woman, utilizes She/Her/Hers pronouns, identifies as gay, and is of Black African descent. She currently does not have children but hopes to in the future. Jamila is an active individual who enjoys reading, hiking, live music, technology, and trail running in her spare time. She is a dog owner, a Leo by zodiac sign, and is characterized as an ENFJ by MBTI typology. Jamila prefers drinking but is not favorable towards smoking, marijuana, or other drugs. She has a preference for women within the ages of 32 and 40 who shares the same viewpoints on alcohol consumption and substances, also values fitness, and is aspiring to have children in the future.
